<div type="definition">
<p>SMALL INSECT which LEAPS and which SUCKS BLOOD.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. A general term for parasites of various kind including a flea is shī 虱.</p>
<p>2. Zǎo 蚤 refers specifically to the flea.</p>
